changelog.insert_last("- Fixed online notification message formatting");
changelog.insert_last("- Removed dead code: comments system, watcher, sound upload");
changelog.insert_last("- Split monolithic chat.bgt into connection.bgt, game.bgt, and chat.bgt");
changelog.insert_last("");
changelog.insert_last("Version 0.4 beta - Obsidian");
changelog.insert_last("- Fixed rules agreement not persisting between sessions");
changelog.insert_last("- Main menu now shows account name and uses cleaner labels");
changelog.insert_last("- Inventory auto-loads on connect, I key opens inventory menu");
changelog.insert_last("- TAB and shift TAB cycling now shows item position");
changelog.insert_last("- Item names display with spaces instead of underscores");
changelog.insert_last("- Escape to disconnect now shows clear countdown feedback");
